  "original_title": "\u0db4\u0dc5\u0dcf\u0dad\u0dca \u0dc4\u0dba\u0d9a\u0da7 \u0dc3\u0dc0\u0dc3 \u0dc0\u0dd0\u0dc3\u0dca\u0dc3",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Evening rain in six provinces",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Department of Meteorology says that rain or thundershowers will occur in Sabaragamuwa, Central, North Central, Uva, South and North West provinces today (29) in the evening or at night.",
        "A spokesperson of the department said that the sky will be cloudy in the northern, central and eastern provinces, while it will rain in the morning in the eastern, Uva and southern provinces.",
        "The spokesperson said that in some places in Sabaragamuwa, Central, North Central, Uva, South, North West and Eastern provinces, more than 75 mm of heavy rain will occur.",
        "The department also states that thunderstorms may be accompanied by lightning and temporary gusty winds."
      ],
